room_title: Escape room "The Lost Temple" by Conundrum Escape Rooms in Durango
room_description: As the favorite students of Old Professor J. you have been entrusted with the final quest he never got to go on. Find The Lost Temple and recover a mystical golden idol for the Professor. Along the way discover what happend to Dr. Robingrove, the last know person to have gone looking for the temple, encounter ancient mysteries, and hopefully escape before the curse of the temple traps you inside forever.
